title: That Metal Show S10E08 Vinnie Paul, Styx.mkv
description: Vinnie Paul returns to That Metal Show to discuss the 20th anniversary re-issue of Pantera's highest-selling album, Vulgar Display of Power, and the latest album from his band Hellyeah, Band of Brothers. Later, Tommy Shaw and James "JY" Young of Styx join up to discuss their latest live release, The Grand Illusion / Pieces of Eight - Live, and their plans to keep on touring. Steve Stevens plays some heavy riffs as the finale's guest guitarist.
